spectroscopy 0.2-1

* Added 2 new functions: epo, fit_bag_plsr

spectroscopy 0.2-0
--------------------------------------------------------------

* Imported many functions from Brendan Malone including `chBLC`, `compspec`, 
  `goof`, `mscBLC`, `snvBLC` and `wavelet_smooth`.
* `munsell_treemap` and `spectra2colour` now accept data.frames.

